## Root Cause Analysis

```bash id="f2q9yq"
User:
Why did Product X experience production delays?

AI:
The delays were mainly caused by:
- Supplier Y delivering raw materials late
- Production utilization exceeding 92%
- Increased demand during the last 2 weeks
```

