#  Core Capabilities

## 🧩 Natural Language Understanding

Users interact using plain English.

No SQL.
No coding.
No technical knowledge required.

---

## 📊 Data-to-Insight Reasoning

The LLM converts raw operational data into:

* explanations,
* summaries,
* insights,
* and recommendations.

---

## 🔍 Root Cause Detection

Instead of only showing metrics, the model explains:

* *why* problems happen,
* *what* caused them,
* and *what* may happen next.

---

## 🧠 Context-Aware Responses

The AI understands relationships between:

* products,
* suppliers,
* sales,
* contracts,
* inventory,
* and production data.

